## Description {#details}

This corresponds to <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/x86addressmode">X86AddressMode</a>, but uses <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sdvalue">SDValue</a>&#39;s instead of register numbers for the leaves of the matched tree.
